<div class="flex min-h-screen bg-gray-50 p-4">
  <main class="w-2/3 pr-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Union-based SQLi 방어 버전</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">파라미터 검증 및 Prepared Statement 사용</p>

      <form action="/lesson/union_sqli_secure/query" method="get" class="space-y-4">
        <label class="block text-gray-700">
          Article ID:
          <input
            name="id"
            type="text"
            value="<%= id %>"
            placeholder="숫자만 입력하세요 (예: 1)"
            required
            class="w-full mt-1 px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring"
          />
        </label>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-green-700 transition"
        >
          안전 조회
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        * 입력값을 정수로만 허용하고, 플레이스홀더에 바인딩하여 SQL Injection을 방어합니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <aside class="w-1/3 pl-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">사용된 SQL</h3>
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-sm">
SELECT id, title
  FROM articles
 WHERE id = ?;
      </pre>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>